Head of Legal, Consumer Banking, Singapore –15+ years PQE
Location:  Singapore
Our client is a household name in the financial services industry, seeking a senior lawyer to head up their consumer banking business. To apply, you must have consumer banking experience (which incorporates wealth management) and understand the regulatory requirements relevant to this business in Singapore. You will also have the ability to confidently manage a small team of lawyers, and deal effectively with external counsel and internal stakeholders. Over and above all this, the successful candidate is someone who will be able to get intimately involved in all aspects of the business, and contribute to the success of the business.
